<tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25508</anchor> <rss>anon.143.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Proof</taxon> <addr>anon.143</addr>  <route>anon.143.xml</route>    </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>The <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverse</link> to <tex>f</tex> is simultaneously a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Sections and retractions">section</link> and a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Sections and retractions">retraction</link>.</p>
</mainmatter> <backmatter><contributions/> <context><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25509</anchor> <rss>erct-003C.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Observation</taxon> <addr>erct-003C</addr>  <route>erct-003C.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>1</month> <day>3</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title><link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">Quasi-invertible</link> maps are <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinvertible</link></title> <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-003C.agda" type="external">erct-003C.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Any <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-invertible</link> map <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> is <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">biinvertible</link>.</p>
 
   
   
 
</mainmatter> </tree></context> <related><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25510</anchor> <rss>erct-000X.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-000X</addr>  <route>erct-000X.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>19</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Quasi-inverse</title> <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000X.agda" type="external">erct-000X.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>A <em><strong>quasi-inverse</strong></em> to a function <tex>f  \colon  A  \to  B</tex> is a function <tex>g  \colon  B  \to  A</tex> equipped with homotopies <tex>\epsilon \colon  f  \circ  g  \sim   1_{ B }</tex> and <tex>\eta \colon  g  \circ  f  \sim 1_{ A }</tex>, rendering <tex>g</tex> simultaneously a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Sections and retractions">section</link> and a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Sections and retractions">retraction</link> of <tex>f</tex>.</p><p>Although no coherence laws are assumed for <tex>\eta</tex> and <tex>\epsilon</tex>, we shall refer to them respectively as the <em>unit</em> and <em>counit</em> of the quasi-inverse.</p></mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25511</anchor> <rss>erct-000Y.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-000Y</addr>  <route>erct-000Y.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>19</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Sections and retractions</title> <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000Y.agda" type="external">erct-000Y.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Let <tex>s  \colon  B  \to  A</tex> and <tex>r  \colon  A  \to  B</tex> be a pair of maps. A homotopy <tex>h  \colon  r \circ  s  \sim   1_{ B }</tex> exhibits <tex>s</tex> as a <em><strong>section</strong></em> of <tex>r</tex> and <tex>r</tex> as a <em><strong>retraction</strong></em> of <tex>s</tex>.</p></mainmatter> </tree></related> <backlinks/> <references/></backmatter></tree>